name: BunnyHopes “the oligarchs”
description:
Infrastructure development through foreign loans which will always be embezzled,  deforestation disguised as economical advancement plans, ratification of laws in order to smoothen their vile political agendas and businesses.
Anyone who tries to prevent or even simply spoke against their wicked objectives will be crushed through slanders, repressive forces, arrests on fabricated charges, kidnappings and even murders.

As long as the greed of the very few overshadowed the needs of the many... 😢
Wake up,
Fight back, 
Rise and rise again... 
Until Lambs become Lions... 😎
